{"tid":336283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[官字兩個口] 港共借一地兩檢租地混淆視聽","createTime":"2017-07-26T10:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T13:15:16.000Z","uid":36184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d728b71c1cc01b3f2b70615fd34f8cb10968a8b","tid":336283,"uid":36184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:07:12.000Z","msg":"班官講極都係用民生、經濟、便利角度去支持一地兩檢係好重要，做唔到就變柒頭直通車<br />\n問題根源係法律角度<br />\n強國袁不斷以&ldquo;符合基本法&rdquo;去解釋，但顯然無客觀準則<br />\n如果香港境內高鐵站某範圍租地比支那係無法律問題，咁他日係咪可以推演到全香港任何地方都租得，然後仲可以用支那法律？<br />\n如果今次港共政府蒙混過關，香港法治將蕩然無存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edef90294a90f9f67e21d89474f367d25a26d3b","tid":336283,"uid":29474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f88615f93c5a3783b3d481532d4294a4a9c157d","tid":336283,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"如果今次港共政府蒙混過關，香港法治將蕩然無存<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDQ糧油時就無左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e15a05af64e37f00cbef0c97e84be6af06781e0","tid":336283,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:59:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果今次港共政府蒙混過關，香港法治將蕩然無存<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDQ糧油時就無左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n神早冇左"},{"pid":"7d82ddf0030be616256fc23f9f5986c43398cded","tid":336283,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T13:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個轉身租哂全香港，行支共法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}